# Example tip content
tip-welcome-title = Welcome to the Station!
tip-welcome-description = Welcome aboard! If you're new, consider asking other crew members for help. Press [color=yellow]Numpad 0[/color] to open the guidebook at any time.

tip-chat-title = Communication Tips
tip-chat-description = Use [color=yellow]T[/color] for local chat, [color=cyan];[/color] for radio, and [color=lime]:[/color] prefix for department channels.

tip-newplayer-title = New Player Guide
tip-newplayer-description = It looks like you're new here! Some helpful tips:
    • Press [color=yellow]Numpad 0[/color] to open the guidebook
    • Use [color=yellow]Z[/color] to activate items in hand
    • Press [color=yellow]Q[/color] to drop items

tip-signlanguage-title = Sign Language
tip-signlanguage-description = You know sign language! Press [color=yellow]J[/color] to open the sign language radial menu and communicate silently with others who understand.

tip-security-title = Security Officer Tips
tip-security-description = As a Security Officer, your job is to [color=yellow]protect and serve[/color] the crew. Remember to always follow Space Law. Your radio prefix is [color=red]:s[/color] for the security channel.

tip-cadet-title = Security Cadet
tip-cadet-description = As a new Security Cadet, stick close to your fellow officers and learn the ropes. Don't be afraid to ask questions! You can access your department’s channel by using using [color=red]:s[/color] in chat.

tip-medical-title = Medical Doctor Tips
tip-medical-description = As a Medical Doctor, check the [color=cyan]health analyzer[/color] for patient status. Your radio prefix is [color=lightblue]:m[/color] for the medical channel.

tip-traitor-title = Syndicate Agent
tip-traitor-description = You are a Syndicate agent. Check your [color=red]uplink[/color] in your PDA (or wherever you were told) to purchase equipment. Complete your objectives and don't get caught!

tip-veteran-title = Thank You!
tip-veteran-description = Thank you for playing! Your dedication to the station is appreciated. Consider helping new players learn the ropes.

tip-nonantag-title = Stay Vigilant
tip-nonantag-description = Keep an eye out for suspicious activity. Report anything unusual to Security.
